299
00:16:58,309 --> 00:16:59,436
Mother, she's beautiful.

300
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:01,771
All the more reason. Mark?

301
00:17:03,273 --> 00:17:05,025
-Colonel Crawford?
- Yes, sir?

302
00:17:05,108 --> 00:17:06,568
Let's get out of this clip joint.

303
00:17:06,609 --> 00:17:08,778
Just a minute, Captain Bailey.

304
00:17:09,779 --> 00:17:10,947
What's the trouble?

305
00:17:11,031 --> 00:17:13,116
Oh, I didn't mean
to bother you with this, General.

306
00:17:13,158 --> 00:17:17,078
