is wanting to take her into the club.

307
00:17:17,495 --> 00:17:19,247
General Webster, sir.

308
00:17:20,415 --> 00:17:23,793
This young lady is one of
Japan's most famous dancers.

309
00:17:24,252 --> 00:17:26,004
She's no ordinary...

310
00:17:26,796 --> 00:17:28,465
Yes, I understand.

311
00:17:30,216 --> 00:17:31,593
