318
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:52,322
that you personally refuse to allow me

319
00:17:52,363 --> 00:17:54,657
to take this young lady into the club?

320
00:17:54,741 --> 00:17:58,995
I understand how you feel, Captain,
and I'm very embarrassed.

321
00:17:59,245 --> 00:18:01,331
But I'm sorry.

322
00:18:01,456 --> 00:18:02,499
Thank you.

323
00:18:02,582 --> 00:18:04,125
Thank you, sir!

324
00:18:04,375 --> 00:18:05,710
Don't you know that there's such a thing

325
