that's expected of you?

477
00:28:54,150 --> 00:28:56,777
Well, I'm certainly going to try,
I'll tell you that.

478
00:28:56,986 --> 00:28:58,404
Well, I don't expect you to marry me

479
00:28:58,487 --> 00:29:00,698
just because it's expected of you.

480
00:29:00,781 --> 00:29:02,199
Listen, you know sometimes I look at you,

481
00:29:02,283 --> 00:29:03,868
and I don't understand you.

482
00:29:03,951 --> 00:29:05,327
I don't know what's going on in your brain.

483
00:29:05,369 --> 00:29:07,705
I think sometimes
I don't even know who you are

484
00:29:07,788 --> 00:29:09,832
or what... Or what you're all about.

485
00:29:10,624 --> 00:29:13,753
