488
00:29:33,147 --> 00:29:36,192
Katsumi, "Wilt thou have this man
to thy wedded husband

489
00:29:36,275 --> 00:29:37,902
"to live together after God's ordinance

490
00:29:37,985 --> 00:29:39,695
